{"tid":602450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拋下金銀衣紙 馬鞍山女子墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-03-23T04:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T04:31:04.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8bdcba67359e021d3ccae624d40425f93b090e","tid":602450,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180323/large/1521774257_bdb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180323%2Flarge%2F1521774257_bdb8.jpg&h=b2d81cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n籃球場地面有一包金銀衣紙及「人字拖」，停車場4樓的石壆則有一件外套。(周鴻熙攝)<br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山富寶花園，早上9時14分，一名30餘歲女子，從多層停車場的高處墮下，倒臥地下籃球場。救援人員接報到場時，女事主昏迷，立即將她送院搶救，惜告不治。籃球場地上有一包金銀衣紙及一對「人字拖」，停車場4樓的石壆則有一件外套，不排除女事主將金銀衣紙掉落樓後再墮下，警方正調查事主身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180323/57983774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57983774&d=wZ8Lq8PGBp3%2BE73tT%2F43J26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=aead2644\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57983774&h=3f5df943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180323/57983774</a>"},{"pid":"4a7b3ba1c17af2e40c21f12010b9105444c6026c","tid":602450,"uid":132302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"未燒收唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n口德 -10000000000"}]}